<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="race-n">race <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /reɪs/    美 /reɪs/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c">1.★ <strong>[C] (速度的) 比赛；竞赛：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>compete in / drop out of a race 
参加/退出比赛</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Finishing this project by December is going to be <strong>a race against time</strong>. 
要在12月之前完成这个项目，我们需要争分夺秒。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-u">2.★ <strong>[U] 竞争：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The race is on to develop more environmentally friendly forms of energy. 
人们正在竞相开发更加环保的能源。</p></div></div>